data\";s:12:\"Translations\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/translations/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/translations/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 18 May 2018 06:54:35 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/?p=52915\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:549:\"<p>You can contribute to Jigoshop eCommerce in a multitude of ways &#8211; and helping with translating it to your language is one of them. You can translate the plugin online via WordPress.org or offline &#8211; using POEdit. WordPress.org: Start by <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/translations/\">Read More</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/translations/\">Translations</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com\">Jigoshop</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Martin Czyz\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6924:\"<p>You can contribute to Jigoshop eCommerce in a multitude of ways &#8211; and helping with translating it to your language is one of them.</p>\n<p>You can translate the plugin online via <a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/projects/wp-plugins/jigoshop-ecommerce\">WordPress.org</a> or offline &#8211; using <a href=\"https://download.poedit.net/Poedit-2.0.4-setup.exe\">POEdit</a>.</p>\n<p>WordPress.org:</p>\n<p>Start by selecting the language you want to translate<br />\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-52917 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P1.png\" srcset=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P1.png 937w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P1-292x300.png 292w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P1-768x790.png 768w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P1-631x649.png 631w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P1-600x617.png 600w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P1-36x36.png 36w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P1-60x62.png 60w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P1-187x192.png 187w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P1-277x285.png 277w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 937px) 100vw, 937px\" /></p>\n<p>Then select the subproject:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Development(trunk) contains all of the phrases from the plugin that will be displayed on your eCommerce site</li>\n<li>Development Readme(trunk) is the plugin&#8217;s readme displayed on WordPress.org</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-52923 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P2.png\" srcset=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P2.png 934w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P2-300x228.png 300w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P2-768x583.png 768w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P2-631x479.png 631w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P2-600x455.png 600w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P2-36x27.png 36w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P2-60x46.png 60w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P2-253x192.png 253w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P2-375x285.png 375w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 934px) 100vw, 934px\" /></p>\n<p>After clicking on the subproject you will be directed to a page that looks like this:<br />\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-52925 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P3.png\" srcset=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P3.png 951w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P3-150x150.png 150w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P3-300x297.png 300w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P3-768x762.png 768w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P3-631x626.png 631w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P3-600x595.png 600w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P3-36x36.png 36w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P3-60x59.png 60w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P3-194x192.png 194w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P3-287x285.png 287w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P3-70x70.png 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 951px) 100vw, 951px\" /></p>\n<p>Double-click on a row in the &#8220;Translation&#8221; column and insert your translation.</p>\n<p>POEdit:<br />\nDownload Jigoshop eCommerce from <a href=\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/jigoshop-ecommerce.zip\">WordPress.org</a> and unzip the file.</p>\n<p>Download and install POEdit. Run the program afterwards. Select &#8220;Create new translation&#8221;.</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-52929 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P4-1.png\" srcset=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P4-1.png 1922w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P4-1-300x164.png 300w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P4-1-768x419.png 768w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P4-1-631x344.png 631w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P4-1-600x327.png 600w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P4-1-36x20.png 36w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P4-1-60x33.png 60w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P4-1-292x159.png 292w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P4-1-522x285.png 522w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1922px) 100vw, 1922px\" /></p>\n<p>Select the location to which you unpacked Jigoshop eCommerce, the .pot file can be found in the &#8220;languages&#8221; catalog:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-52931 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P5.png\" srcset=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P5.png 1919w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P5-300x164.png 300w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P5-768x420.png 768w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P5-631x345.png 631w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P5-600x328.png 600w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P5-36x20.png 36w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P5-60x33.png 60w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P5-292x160.png 292w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P5-521x285.png 521w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1919px) 100vw, 1919px\" /></p>\n<p>Select the language you&#8217;re translating to:<br />\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-52933 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P6.png\" srcset=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P6.png 1919w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P6-300x164.png 300w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P6-768x419.png 768w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P6-631x345.png 631w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P6-600x328.png 600w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P6-36x20.png 36w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P6-60x33.png 60w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P6-292x159.png 292w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/P6-522x285.png 522w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1919px) 100vw, 1919px\" /></p>\n<p>At the bottom you can see two text inputs, one of them is &#8220;Translation&#8221; &#8211; you can enter your translation there.</p>\n<p>After saving you can send the translated file to support@jigoshop.com for verification. Thanks!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/translations/\">Translations</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com\">Jigoshop</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/translations/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"40+ new themes on jigoshop.com!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/40-new-themes-jigoshop-com/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/40-new-themes-jigoshop-com/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 09 Feb 2018 12:44:09 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/?p=53139\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:603:\"<p>&#160; Attractive and functional design of your web store plays a crucial role in successful online sales. It increases the perceived value of your products and works to make your website and business seem more trustworthy. While establishing your online <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/40-new-themes-jigoshop-com/\">Read More</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/40-new-themes-jigoshop-com/\">40+ new themes on jigoshop.com!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com\">Jigoshop</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Jigoshop eCommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8572:\"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Attractive and functional design of your web store plays a crucial role in successful online sales. It increases the perceived value of your products and works to make your website and business seem more trustworthy.</p>\n<p>While establishing your online shop you might worry that great design or redesign of your webpage can consume many resources. Thankfully you are mistaken! As Jigoshop eCommerce enjoyer you have the advantage of using many, stylish, functional and what&#8217;s most important free themes created by the WordPress community. We created an overview of some, to show you how many great options are there!</p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Illdy</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Illdy is a stunning multipurpose WordPress theme built based on Bootstrap frontend framework making it fully responsive and mobile friendly. This leaves the heavy lifting to WordPress Customizer, therefore, you can create your website on live preview mode. Which means that you can see changes happen on your website in real time as you make them.</p>\n<p> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-53197 size-large\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Illdy-631x473.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"631\" height=\"473\" srcset=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Illdy-631x473.jpg 631w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Illdy-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Illdy-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Illdy-600x450.jpg 600w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Illdy-36x27.jpg 36w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Illdy-60x45.jpg 60w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Illdy-256x192.jpg 256w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Illdy-380x285.jpg 380w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Illdy.jpg 1142w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 631px) 100vw, 631px\" /></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Fluida</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Fluida is a modern, crystal clear and squeaky clean theme. It shines bright with a fluid and responsive layout and carries under its hood a light and powerful framework. Fluida also provides over 100 customizer theme settings that enable you to take full control of your site.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-53155 size-large\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Azera-Shop-631x473.png\" alt=\"theme Azera Shop new template jigoshop ecommerce\" width=\"631\" height=\"473\" srcset=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Azera-Shop-631x473.png 631w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Azera-Shop-300x225.png 300w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Azera-Shop-768x576.png 768w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Azera-Shop-600x450.png 600w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Azera-Shop-36x27.png 36w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Azera-Shop-60x45.png 60w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Azera-Shop-256x192.png 256w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Azera-Shop-380x285.png 380w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Azera-Shop.png 880w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 631px) 100vw, 631px\" /></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Athena</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Athena is a feature-loaded, user-friendly, fully responsive, Parallax modern WordPress theme built with care and SEO in mind. Athena features a full-width frontpage slider, animated callouts with over 600 icons to choose from. Athena allows you to fully customize your site without having to work with the code. Azera Shop</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-53153 size-large\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Athena-631x473.jpg\" alt=\"theme athena new template jigoshop ecommerce\" width=\"631\" height=\"473\" srcset=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Athena-631x473.jpg 631w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Athena-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Athena-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Athena-600x450.jpg 600w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Athena-36x27.jpg 36w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Athena-60x45.jpg 60w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Athena-256x192.jpg 256w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Athena-380x285.jpg 380w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Athena.jpg 1142w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 631px) 100vw, 631px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Llorix One Lite</h1>\n<div class=\"theme-info\">\n<div class=\"theme-description entry-summary\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Llorix One Lite is a free and beautiful one-page business WordPress theme, with a flat and clean bootstrap based design and an elegant parallax effect. It provides a simple, minimal and modern look that can be used for any kind of personal businesses or startup mobile app.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-53185 size-large\" style=\"text-align: center;\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Llorix-One-light-631x473.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"631\" height=\"473\" srcset=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Llorix-One-light-631x473.png 631w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Llorix-One-light-300x225.png 300w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Llorix-One-light-768x576.png 768w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Llorix-One-light-600x450.png 600w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Llorix-One-light-36x27.png 36w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Llorix-One-light-60x45.png 60w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Llorix-One-light-256x192.png 256w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Llorix-One-light-380x285.png 380w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Llorix-One-light.png 880w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 631px) 100vw, 631px\" /></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Zerif Lite</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Zerif LITE is a free one page WordPress theme. It&#8217;s perfect for web agency business, corporate business, personal and parallax business portfolio, photography sites and freelancer. It&#8217;s built on BootStrap with parallax support. It&#8217;s responsive, clean, modern, flat and minimal.</p>\n</div>\n<h3 lang=\"en-US\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-53201 size-large\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/images-Zerif1-631x317.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"631\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/images-Zerif1-631x317.jpg 631w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/images-Zerif1-300x151.jpg 300w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/images-Zerif1-768x386.jpg 768w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/images-Zerif1-600x301.jpg 600w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/images-Zerif1-36x18.jpg 36w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/images-Zerif1-60x30.jpg 60w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/images-Zerif1-292x147.jpg 292w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/images-Zerif1-567x285.jpg 567w, https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/images-Zerif1.jpg 880w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 631px) 100vw, 631px\" /></h3>\n<h2 lang=\"en-US\"></h2>\n<h2 lang=\"en-US\">There&#8217;s much more!</h2>\n<p>In overall we&#8217;ve added 45 themes to our webpage &#8211; all functional, attractive, free and Jigoshop eCommerce compatible! New years is coming, maybe it&#8217;s time to refresh the look of your store? Which of the templates caught your eye?</p>\n<p>You will find them all <a href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/product-category/themes/\">HERE</a>!</p>\n<h3 lang=\"en-US\">Give us a shout!</h3>\n<p>If you have any questions, problems, ideas or suggestions give us a shout at <a href=\"mailto:support@jigoshop.com\">support@jigoshop.com</a> or our social media @jigoshop! All the improvements are mostly possible thanks to you – our users! Your input helps us develop our software to high standards and identify and fix many bugs.</p>\n</div>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/40-new-themes-jigoshop-com/\">40+ new themes on jigoshop.com!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com\">Jigoshop</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/40-new-themes-jigoshop-com/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"We’re offering help with migration from Jigoshop 1.x/WooCommerce to Jigoshop eCommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:110:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/offering-help-migration-jigoshop-1-x-woocommerce-jigoshop-ecommerce/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:119:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/offering-help-migration-jigoshop-1-x-woocommerce-jigoshop-ecommerce/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 02 Jan 2018 14:36:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/?p=53605\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:757:\"<p>&#160; As you might have noticed &#8211; some of our users have experienced issues with the migration from Jigoshop 1.x and/or WooCommerce to Jigoshop eCommerce. These issues can be divided into the following categories: 1. Database record malformations 2. Insecure <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/offering-help-migration-jigoshop-1-x-woocommerce-jigoshop-ecommerce/\">Read More</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/offering-help-migration-jigoshop-1-x-woocommerce-jigoshop-ecommerce/\">We&#8217;re offering help with migration from Jigoshop 1.x/WooCommerce to Jigoshop eCommerce</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com\">Jigoshop</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Martin Czyz\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3293:\"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>As you might have noticed &#8211; some of our users have experienced issues with the migration from Jigoshop 1.x and/or WooCommerce to Jigoshop eCommerce. These issues can be divided into the following categories:</p>\n<p>1. Database record malformations<br />\n2. Insecure functionality implementations<br />\n3. Design changes after the update</p>\n<p>In the case of the first category &#8211; since the data in the database is malformed/missing &#8211; there&#8217;s not much we can do &#8211; we can try to restore the missing data, but your best guess is to restore the site from the backup created prior to the migration and contact Jigoshop&#8217;s Support Team (support@jigoshop.com) &#8211; we&#8217;ll try to help you with the migration and it&#8217;s covered in the free support package.</p>\n<p>The second case&#8217;s different &#8211; it&#8217;s mostly caused by the theme&#8217;s developer (sometimes a separate developer, that implemented a custom functionality) not using an additional condition to determine if a function/variable/class exists &#8211; in layman&#8217;s terms &#8211; the developer did not check for the existence of a module before calling it. This results mostly in blank pages (fatal errors).</p>\n<p>The last can be divided into two subcategories: one&#8217;s fairly simple &#8211; the CSS stylesheet does not contain the appropriate selector and thus the styling does not apply to the element it should or the styling defaults to Jigoshop eCommerce&#8217;s default style. The second one&#8217;s a bit more complicated &#8211; if you used the Migration Information Tool from Jigoshop 1.x this might sound familiar &#8211; the customized templates used in Jigoshop 1.x or WooCommerce are not being used in Jigoshop eCommerce, which results in the pages looking differently.</p>\n<p>The last two cases are not covered by the free support package, but we decided to provide our users with the option of purchasing a migration package. Obviously, some websites can be very simple where others are very sophisticated. If the workload required to properly migrate the site exceeds 16 human hours you will need to receive a quote for the work required. However, all the migrations which can be done within 16 hours will be covered under the set price of $200 + VAT (if applicable).</p>\n<p>In the case of migrating WooCommerce to Jigoshop eCommerce &#8211; the migration tool is available for free here, at jigoshop.com, but in the case of your WooCommerce plugins/custom functionality &#8211; we&#8217;ll be charging $300 for standard migrations, and we&#8217;ll give you a quote if the workload exceeds 24 human hours.</p>\n<p>If you have any questions, problems, ideas or suggestions give us a shout at support@jigoshop.com, they are very valuable to us! All the improvements are mostly possible thanks to you – our users! Your input helps us develop our software to high standards and identify and fix many bugs.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/offering-help-migration-jigoshop-1-x-woocommerce-jigoshop-ecommerce/\">We&#8217;re offering help with migration from Jigoshop 1.x/WooCommerce to Jigoshop eCommerce</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com\">Jigoshop</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:115:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/offering-help-migration-jigoshop-1-x-woocommerce-jigoshop-ecommerce/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:112:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"Want Jigoshop eCommerce in your language? Translations needed!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/want-jigoshop-ecommerce-language-translations/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:97:\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/want-jigoshop-ecommerce-language-translations/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s