explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:678:\"<p>Hi Jigoshoppers! For the last two weeks we were working on the release of Jigoshop eCommerce v. 2.1, thus the lack of blog posts 😉 . Even though we were quite busy with the latest release, we managed to release quite <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/extension-updates-stable-releases-jigoshop-ecommerce-4142017/\">Read More</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/extension-updates-stable-releases-jigoshop-ecommerce-4142017/\">Extension Updates – Stable Releases for Jigoshop eCommerce (4/14/2017)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com\">Jigoshop</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Martin Czyz\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2537:\"<h2>Hi Jigoshoppers!</h2>\n<p>For the last two weeks we were working on the release of Jigoshop eCommerce v. 2.1, thus the lack of blog posts 😉 . Even though we were quite busy with the latest release, we managed to release quite a few Jigoshop eCommerce compatible extensions.  The next round is coming soon, so you might want to consider visiting our Facebook Page, as well as keeping track of our blog entries here, at jigoshop.com :).<br />\nOh, and by the way &#8211; If you notice any potential bugs <a href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/contact/\">contact<br />\nus</a> &#8211; your feedback is very important to us :).<span id=\"more-51853\"></span></p>\n<h2>Recently Updated Extensions</h2>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/product/jigoshop-worldpay-card-file-payments/\"><br />\n<img style=\"height: 30%; width: 30%; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/worldpaycof.png\" /><br />\nWorldPay Card On File Payments<br />\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/product/jigoshop-simplify-commerce-mastercard/\"><br />\n<img style=\"height: 30%; width: 30%; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/simplify.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\nSimplify Commerce by Mastercard<br />\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/product/jigoshop-sofort-payment-gateway/\"><br />\n<img style=\"height: 30%; width: 30%; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sofortj.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\nSOFORT Payment Gateway<br />\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/product/jigoshop-tpay-com-payment-gateway/\"><br />\n<img style=\"height: 30%; width: 30%; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/tpay.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\ntpay.com Payment Gateway<br />\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/product/jigoshop-mollie-payment-gateway/\"><br />\n<img style=\"height: 30%; width: 30%; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;\" src=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/molliej.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\nMollie Payment Gateway<br />\n</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com/development/post/extension-updates-stable-releases-jigoshop-ecommerce-4142017/\">Extension Updates – Stable Releases for Jigoshop eCommerce (4/14/2017)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.jigoshop.com\">Jigoshop</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\