(35, 1, '2019-08-07 12:57:03', '2019-08-07 16:57:03', 'Power your run with the FuelCell Rebel women\'s running shoe. These shoes match their aggressive look with a responsive ride that feels faster-than-fast. The speed-seeking bootie construction with double jacquard forefoot offers a sleek, breathable fit.', 'New Balance J03', '<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Deconstructed Heel Counter</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>FuelCell foam delivers a propulsive feel to help drive you forward</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Trace Fiber</strong></li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'new-balance-j03', '', '', '2019-08-07 13:47:08', '2019-08-07 17:47:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=35', 0, 'product', '', 0),
