(40, 1, '2019-08-07 13:00:40', '2019-08-07 17:00:40', 'Meet our ultimate all-weather road runner that’s engineered with GORE-TEX® technology: The D33. Made with a fitted waterproof GORE-TEX® Invisible Fit upper, this shoe delivers a close-to-foot fit with less bulk than the traditional GORETEX® waterproof membrane. It’s responsive with a TruFuse dual-foam midsole system that provides a dynamic fusion of cushioning and durability that’s engineered to rack up serious mileage.', 'New Balance D33', '<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>No sew material application</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Synthetic upper</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Blown rubber forefoot</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Invisible fit</strong></li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'new-balance-d33', '', '', '2019-08-07 13:00:41', '2019-08-07 17:00:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=40', 0, 'product', '', 0),
